thread.title_full: Season's last farmers market in Libertyville

author: Daily Herald report
title: Season's last farmers market in Libertyville
text:
Maria Mandarino, chef from The Green Room, downtown Libertyville's "world bistro" will be featured at 10:30 a.m., Thursday, Oct. 22, for the final food demonstration of the season at MainStreet Libertyville's Farmers Market. As she does at the restaurant, Mandarino will use fresh produce, blending comfort food from numerous cultures with haute cuisine using fresh, hand-selected ingredients. It also is the market's final day for 2015 and runs from 7 a.m. to 1 p.m. on Church Street just west of Milwaukee Avenue. Call (847) 680-0336 or visit www.libertyvillefarmersmarket.org .
